  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize marker_seen: switch to marker_track state immediately when marker is detected.",
    "In marker_track, use move_to_marker as the only controllable; if marker_lost, switch to scan_full to reacquire.",
    "If marker_close occurs in any state, transition to goal_stop and only allow stop.",
    "After encountering obstacles, always pass through a scan_full state before resuming exploration.",
    "In obs_left, prefer rotate_clockwise; in obs_right, prefer rotate_counterclockwise, to avoid oscillations.",
    "In search (scan_full), alternate between short forward moves and scans to maximize marker reacquisition chances.",
    "Never allow move_forward from obs_front; always require recovery via scan_full.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled deterministically and safely, with self-loops for non-critical events in commit/action states.",
    "Helper states ensure one-shot actions and prevent infinite controllable loops."
  ]
